Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.92,0:00:29.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,縢失踪了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.71,0:00:34.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,二室也有个执行官趁乱潜逃了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.76,0:00:37.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,监视官
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.80,0:00:40.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,縢不会潜逃的吧？
